 "name": "RPlog_Muun_Money_Minute_-_Greater_Javin",
 "title": "Muun Money Minute: Greater Javin",
 "summary": "In the luxurious lobby of the Yarith Hotel on Cloud City, the cobalt-haired promoter Quinne Stardust Rose, arm in a sling, prepares for a live InterGalactic News financial segment hosted by the golden-skinned economist anchor Professor Brackett and her producer-cameraman Gym. The proceedings are repeatedly upstaged by the hapless Quarren engineer Druze, who spectacularly spills a buffet's worth of seafood delicacies and frets over his dignity. Once the cameras roll, Quinne plays the consummate professional, touting Cloud City's economic resilience after the recent attack, the late Johanna's support for the miners, Presav Crestian Tarasar's influence, and the relocated Greater Javin Medical Society conference, delivering a polished promotional interview.",
